metadata.name: Anthology
metadata.description:
What is a god? An entity that creates. An artist is not very different from this. It sounds irreverent and a bit strange, I know. But tall! Think about it. An artist creates, transmits his inner world in a piece, captures his being, his essence and then launches it into the world like a small child in search of a new home.

This piece marks a beginning and after. Are you the one who will give him a home?
